You take care of that thing?

1765
01:59:42,251 --> 01:59:43,377
Oh.

1766
01:59:48,466 --> 01:59:50,468
-Thanks.
-Yeah, you owe me 75 bucks.

1767
01:59:51,427 --> 01:59:54,138
Seventy-five? Charlie said 60.

1768
01:59:54,180 --> 01:59:56,849
Oh. I'm doing this for free?

1769
01:59:58,976 --> 02:00:02,521
-[chuckles]
-Hey, Tony. Tony, tell us about the trip.

1770
02:00:02,563 --> 02:00:05,274
-You've been gone two months.
-Yeah, how was he, the tootsoon?

1771
02:00:05,316 --> 02:00:08,444
-He get on your nerves?
-Don't call him that.

1772
02:00:08,486 --> 02:00:11,405
<i>♪ Santa Claus is coming </i>♪

1773
02:00:11,447 --> 02:00:13,157
<i>♪ To town... </i>♪

1774
02:00:13,199 --> 02:00:14,283
All right.

1775
02:00:17,453 --> 02:00:19,955
Tony, you should have seen
the day last week.

1776
02:00:19,997 --> 02:00:24,502
Little Frankie climbed up onto the TV.
I took a picture of him, it was so cute.

1777
