-Did he break it?
-You're thinking of toasters.

1780
02:00:33,260 --> 02:00:35,721
You can't get electrocuted
from the TV set!

1781
02:00:35,763 --> 02:00:38,933
She's not thinking about a toaster.
She's thinking about a TV!

1782
02:00:38,974 --> 02:00:40,976
-Is she taking it into the bathtub?
-[loud chatter]

1783
02:00:41,018 --> 02:00:44,105
-[arguing continues]
-[knocking]

1784
02:00:44,146 --> 02:00:47,483
-[man] You're not gonna get electrocuted.
-[arguing continues]

1785
02:00:51,612 --> 02:00:55,116
-Charlie!
-Hey, Lip. Johnny invited me.

1786
02:00:55,157 --> 02:00:58,244
-Oh. Well, come on in.
-[laughs] All right.

1787
02:00:58,285 --> 02:00:59,995
Oh. You remember Marie?

