-Hey, Marie.
-Charlie, you actually came?

1789
02:01:02,790 --> 02:01:05,000
-I was kidding!
-[laughs]

1790
02:01:05,042 --> 02:01:07,545
-With the wife, too? Geez.
-Merry Christmas.

1791
02:01:07,586 --> 02:01:09,588
-Get in here.
-Merry Christmas, hello.

1792
02:01:09,630 --> 02:01:11,424
What a surprise. Nice to see you.

1793
02:01:11,465 --> 02:01:14,718
[Johnny] Everybody, Charlie
from the pawnshop. Didn't bring nothing.

1794
02:01:14,760 --> 02:01:17,054
Christmas. Can you believe it?
Come here. Sit down.

1795
02:01:17,096 --> 02:01:19,306
[man] Sit down, sit down.

1796
02:01:19,348 --> 02:01:21,308
[soft music fades in]

1797
