Doc. [laughs]

1798
02:01:28,274 --> 02:01:30,443
Ah. Welcome.

1799
02:01:30,484 --> 02:01:32,069
[Tony] Oh.

1800
02:01:33,404 --> 02:01:35,489
-[chatter]
-[Tony] Hey, everybody!

1801
02:01:35,531 --> 02:01:39,326
-[man] Stop it, stop it.
-This is Dr Donald Shirley.

1802
02:01:42,246 --> 02:01:43,289
Merry Christmas.

1803
02:01:43,330 --> 02:01:47,626
<i>♪ Yuletide carols
Being sung by a choir... </i>♪

1804
02:01:47,668 --> 02:01:50,337
Well, come on. Make some room.
Get this man a plate!

1805
02:01:50,379 --> 02:01:52,339
[lively chatter resumes]

1806
02:01:56,051 --> 02:01:57,011
[quietly] Oh.

1807
02:01:57,720 --> 02:01:59,597
<i>♪ Turkey and some mistletoe... </i>♪

1808
