-Hello.
-You must be Dolores.

1809
02:02:02,641 --> 02:02:03,768
Welcome.

1810
02:02:03,809 --> 02:02:05,811
<i>-Buon Natale.</i>
-[Dolores laughs]

1811
02:02:07,396 --> 02:02:09,398
Thank you for sharing
your husband with me.

1812
02:02:16,447 --> 02:02:19,158
[quietly] Thank you
for helping him with the letters.

1813
02:02:21,577 --> 02:02:23,204
[laughs]

